<step outcome="successful">And [Assertion] Verify IG &apos;TravelCalculationPricesTable&apos; has an empty inserted row</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Progress] I wait for &apos;5&apos; sec</step>
<step outcome="ignorable">!-- And [Input] I click on &apos;TravelCalculationPricesSaveButton&apos;</step>
<step outcome="ignorable">!-- And [Input] I click on &apos;TravelCalculationPricesSaveButton&apos;</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Input] I click on &apos;TravelCalculationPricesSaveButton&apos; and if &apos;AlertDialog&apos; not appear reclick</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Assertion] Verify &apos;AlertMsgBody&apos; contains &apos;p:CorrectErrorsBeforeSaving&apos; text</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Input] I click on &apos;OkButton&apos;</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Navigation] I reload page</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Progress] I wait for &apos;7&apos; sec</step>
<step outcome="successful">Then [Input] I click on &apos;UserDDL&apos;</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Input] I click on &apos;LogoutButton&apos;</step>
<step outcome="successful">And [Assertion] Verify &apos;loginButton&apos; is present</step>
</scenario>
